Study
Liveness: restart container if failing.
Readiness: remove from service endpoints if failing.
Startup: gate liveness for slow-starting apps.
Handlers: httpGet, tcpSocket, exec, grpc.

Hands-On
livenessProbe:
  httpGet: {path: /healthz, port: 8080}
  initialDelaySeconds: 10
  periodSeconds: 10
readinessProbe:
  httpGet: {path: /ready, port: 8080}
  periodSeconds: 5
startupProbe:
  httpGet: {path: /healthz, port: 8080}
  failureThreshold: 30
  periodSeconds: 10Make a probe fail intentionally; observe pod restarts / endpoint removal.

